caption:
🎉✨ Happy 4th Birthday to my girl, Lily! ✨🎉

How is it possible you’re FOUR already?! Feels like you were just learning to crawl and now you’re running the whole house (and my heart) like it’s your job. You’re sweet, wild, hilarious, and already cooler than I’ll ever be.

Thank you for making life louder, messier, and a million times more fun. I’m the luckiest to be your Dad and watch you grow into the little superstar you are. Keep shining, kiddo. 🌈🦄

Here’s to all the giggles, dance parties, and snack attacks coming your way this year. Love you forever, even when you steal all my snacks. 💜

#HappyBirthday #LilyTurns4 #GirlDad #ProudParent #GrowingUpTooFast
